               Confined Six Months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>KEATING - <rs id="t18280221-283-verdict1499" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18280221-283-verdict1499" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 17.</p>
